title: Pirelli Calendar 2010 (South Florida PBS)
overview: Join acclaimed photographer Terry Richardson and a cast of world-renowned models as they embark on a vibrant and playful journey to create the 2010 Pirelli Calendar. Set against the stunning backdrop of Bahia, Brazil, this behind-the-scenes video offers an intimate glimpse into the artistic process and the dynamic energy of the shoot.  The video introduces the star-studded lineup of models—Miranda Kerr, Ana Beatriz Barros, Lily Cole, Daisy Lowe, and Marloes Horst—each bringing their unique charm and personality to the project.
